title: Elena Rybakina
summary: Elena Andreyevna Rybakina (Russian: Елена Андреевна Рыбакина, lit. 'jɪˈlʲenə rɨˈbakʲɪnə', born 17 June 1999) is a Russian-born Kazakhstani professional tennis player. She has a career-high ranking of No. 14 by the Women's Tennis Association (WTA). Rybakina has reached seven finals on the WTA Tour, winning two titles, including one at the Premier level.
